@node About "About Presentation Master and this Help file"
 This Help capability utilizes the AmigaGuide system provided by
 @{" Commodore " link G_Commodore} and written by David Junod.  Thanks to both Commodore
 and David for such a fine hyper-help system.

 If you wish, you can add to this file yourself by using a text
 editor.  Contact Commodore for documentation if necessary, or simply
 follow the existing file as an example.  As you discover items which
 you would like to always have at your fingertips, add them to this
 file so they will always be there.  Just make sure that you keep the
 original file on a backup disk so if you damage the file you can at
 least return to the original.  Also, if you think your additions are
 of interest to others, call Oxxi and let us know what you have done.
 Just remember that this file is copyrighted so you cannot give out
 copies to others, even if you have modified it, without written
 permission from Oxxi.

 This file was derived by an evolutionary growth process, adding
 information as it was thought of.  Therefore, all areas are not covered
 to the same level of depth.  We apologize for this, but are happy
 that such a comprehensive on-line documentation could be provided.
@endnode

@node Piracy
 Presentation Master has been designed with ease of expansion as one
 of its goals.  It is very modular and new modules will be released in
 the future which will enhance and expand the program capabilities.
 The intent is to develop Presentation Master into a system which
 provides all useful charting types as well as many more object
 creation capabilities.  In addition the output modules will be
 expanded to provide more quality output capabilities to a wider
 variety of output devices.  However, this expansion will not come
 unless the consumer community supports the product.

 Please honor our commitment to a quality product by not giving out
 copies to others.  The only way that this can remain a top-level
 product is through continuing development.  The only way that
 development will continue will be if the product generates revenue for
 Oxxi and its developers.  Piracy severly affects this revenue and has
 been directly responsible for development stopping on many fine products.
 Please don't contribute to the criminal community of software pirates.
@endnode

@node Introduction

             Oxxi Presentation Master             @{" Acknowledgements " link Acknowledgements}

 Presentation Master is a complete Presentation Authoring Environment.
 You can rough out your presentation from the top down, starting with
 slides for general categories, adding subordinated slides as the
 direction of your presentation becomes clear, and finally adding text,
 graphics, animation - the details - to carry your full message.

 Presentation Master goes far beyond the capabilities of a slide show
 program, adding text, graphics and data import, business graphing,
 output to @{" PostScript " link PostScript} and Amiga print devices, plus a full array of
 features designed to make your presentation communicate on all the
 levels multi-media makes possible.

 Presentation Master works as a graphical outlining system.  The
 visual outline is an integral part of the final structure of your
 presentation.  With Presentation Master, you can create complete,
 finished presentations faster and more effectively than with any
 other presentaion system available today.

 Presentation Master is Suitable for:
    Business Graphics
      The premier program on the Amiga computer for business
      presentation graphics.
    Video Presentations and Storyboarding
      The most convenient interface for video storyboarding.
      Enjoy the convenience of a fully integrated environment
      with draw abilities, titling, animation, and slideshow
      all in one package.
    Illustration and Drawing
      A uniquely powerful object based draw program.
    Animation
      The first object based draw program with keyframe animation.
    Plus much more...
@endnode

